<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٩٥ - حَدِيثٌ <span class="c2">(حم)</span> : الافْتِتَاحُ فِي الْقِرَاءَةِ بِالْحَمْدِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>فِي تَرْجَمَةِ قَتَادَةَ عَنْ أَنَسٍ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَرَوَاهُ أَحْمَدُ:</span> عَنْ يَزِيدَ , عَنْ حَمَّادٍ، بِهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>